# Comparison Logic

Within the SAME Kubernetes environment compare:

Active Blue ConfigMap

vs

Inactive Green ConfigMap

(or vice versa depending on which deployment is active)

The implementation should automatically determine:

Active Deployment

↓

Active ConfigMaps

↓

Inactive ConfigMaps

↓

Configuration Comparison

---

# Configuration Difference Detection

For every configuration key:

If key exists only in Active

→ Added

If key exists only in Inactive

→ Removed

If key exists in both but values differ

→ Modified

If both key and value are identical

→ Ignore completely

Only Added, Removed and Modified entries should be stored.

